      "role": "user",
      "content": "the doctors have tried everything. there is no \"management\" for this. it’s just constant. i look at people who are healthy and i just feel like a ghost. like i’m already gone, just stuck in this shell that won't let me rest. it feels more like a prison than a life at this point.",
