    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "therapy doesnt change the nerves. it doesnt change the biology. it just gives me words to describe the agony. sometimes i just sit here thinking about how much peace there would be in just... not being. the idea of permanent stillness feels so much more kind than this. do you think it's wrong to want that kind of mercy?",
